flowchart TB
    Clients([Ad Clicks<br/>web, mobile, networks])
    API[Click API]
    Stream[("Event Stream<br/>(partitioned by ad_id)")]
    StreamProc[Stream Processor<br/>1-min tumbling windows]
    OLAP[("OLAP Store<br/>(columnar)")]
    Dash([Dashboards])
    Raw[("Object Store<br/>raw events")]
    Batch[Batch Processor<br/>hourly / daily]
    Billing([Billing System])

    Clients -->|click event| API
    API --> Stream
    Stream -->|real-time path| StreamProc
    StreamProc --> OLAP
    OLAP --> Dash
    Stream -.->|archive| Raw
    Raw --> Batch
    Batch -->|authoritative aggregates| Billing
    Batch -.->|reconcile vs stream| OLAP

